    "name": "The Fat Cat Fest",
    "steam_appid": 3259080,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >『The Fat Cat Fest』是一款两人一起玩的派对游戏。让我们一边大笑，一边挑战吃饭比赛和各种有趣的小游戏吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从五只毛茸茸的可爱伙伴中挑选你最喜欢的猫咪，一起加入欢乐派对吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>吃啊吃，尽情吃个够，夺取胜利吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在尽情享用哥伦比亚特色美食的同时，与朋友一较高下吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最先吃完的人就是赢家！别忘了提前空好肚子哦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259080/extras/0776fc1e2d510fefd35f0c628c4d6068.poster.avif?t=1762797756\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259080/extras/0776fc1e2d510fefd35f0c628c4d6068.webm?t=1762797756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259080/extras/0776fc1e2d510fefd35f0c628c4d6068.mp4?t=1762797756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>就连吃饭的空档也能用迷你游戏一决高下！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用餐间隙期间，将有随机出现的7种迷你游戏等待着你！在此拉开差距，最终夺取王者宝座吧！<br>迷你游戏节奏飞快、对局短暂。虽然规则简单易懂，但要占据优势却非易事。<br>想赢的话，直到最后一刻都绝不能松懈！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259080/extras/76aa2344279417ae44448f371338c21e.poster.avif?t=1762797756\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259080/extras/76aa2344279417ae44448f371338c21e.webm?t=1762797756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259080/extras/76aa2344279417ae44448f371338c21e.mp4?t=1762797756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>连猫咪都能懂！简单操作</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仅需一根摇杆与一个按键，就能吃遍全场！操作简单到连我家的猫咪都能轻松掌握！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然推荐使用两个手柄进行游戏，但仅用一个键盘也能畅玩。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259080/extras/b56df7f1078d6cb1a325bc9259238919.poster.avif?t=1762797756\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259080/extras/b56df7f1078d6cb1a325bc9259238919.webm?t=1762797756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259080/extras/b56df7f1078d6cb1a325bc9259238919.mp4?t=1762797756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>快来认识一下猫咪伙伴们！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Timmy                                                            Miguel</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259080/extras/96cf2271ae96baa73d5faa579480d2a0.avif?t=1762797756\" width=564 height=243 /></span><strong> </strong><br> <strong>Chad                                                                           Cejon</strong><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259080/extras/acdc665d4604666d61654e588860141c.avif?t=1762797756\" width=600 height=350 /></span></h2>",
